<div class="content-page">
  <h1>About LighterMe</h1>

  <h2>Our Mission</h2>
  <p>LighterMe exists for one reason: to help women in the UK find safe, effective, clinician-led weight management programmes.</p>

  <p>The weight loss industry is full of noise — fad diets, unregulated supplements, and misleading claims. We believe you deserve better. You deserve clear, honest information about programmes that are led by qualified clinicians and regulated by UK authorities.</p>

  <h2>What We Do</h2>
  <p>We research, verify, and compare UK weight management programmes so you don't have to. Every clinic listed on LighterMe has been individually verified for:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Clinical oversight</strong> — programmes led by qualified healthcare professionals</li>
    <li><strong>UK regulation</strong> — operating within UK healthcare standards</li>
    <li><strong>Transparent pricing</strong> — clear about costs and what's included</li>
    <li><strong>Patient support</strong> — ongoing care, not just one-off consultations</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How We Make Money</h2>
  <p>Full transparency: LighterMe earns a commission when you visit a clinic through our links and sign up for a programme. This is called affiliate marketing.</p>

  <p>Here's what's important:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>You never pay more because you came through our link</li>
    <li>Our commission comes from the clinic, not from you</li>
    <li>We only list clinics we've independently verified</li>
    <li>We will never recommend a programme just because it pays a higher commission</li>
  </ul>

  <p>We believe this model aligns our interests with yours: we only earn when we connect you with a programme that's genuinely worth your time.</p>

  <p>For full details, see our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a>.</p>

  <h2>Our Values</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Honesty first</strong> — We will never use misleading claims or exaggerated promises</li>
    <li><strong>Compliance always</strong> — We follow MHRA, ASA, and UK GDPR regulations to the letter</li>
    <li><strong>Women-centred</strong> — We understand that women's weight management needs are different</li>
    <li><strong>Evidence-based</strong> — We only share information backed by medical evidence</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Have a question, suggestion, or concern? We'd love to hear from you.</p>
  <p>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@lighterme.co.uk">hello@lighterme.co.uk</a></p>
</div>

